Open the door!

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:21.879
Let me out!

00:08:45.159 --> 00:08:45.960
A ghost!

00:08:47.679 --> 00:08:48.960
Look how scared you are.

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:53.840
And then what happened?

00:08:54.679 --> 00:08:57.039
I heard this from the Imperial Guards.

00:08:57.519 --> 00:08:58.720
It seems the Second Young Master

00:08:58.919 --> 00:09:01.399
may not escape Soul Reaping by the Ghost King.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:06.480
Is there any way to save my brother?

00:09:07.679 --> 00:09:09.440
Don't be foolish, Princess Yue.

00:09:09.759 --> 00:09:10.799
Everyone has their own fate.

00:09:11.080 --> 00:09:13.480
So many powerful warriors and extraordinary people

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:14.840
still can't figure it out.

00:09:14.919 --> 00:09:16.320
They can't handle those monsters.

00:09:16.879 --> 00:09:18.240
You're just a young woman.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:20.039
What could you possibly do?

00:09:21.200 --> 00:09:24.919
Can you trade your life for the Second Young Master?

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:30.080
Lord Father.

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:32.000
You called us here late at night

00:09:32.279 --> 00:09:34.000
because of the rumors about Soul Reaping by the Ghost King?

00:09:34.279 --> 00:09:35.080
That's right.

00:09:35.799 --> 00:09:38.320
It's no longer just a rumor.

00:09:38.799 --> 00:09:40.320
The one killed in the Ghost King Temple

00:09:41.120 --> 00:09:43.840
was Eunuch Tong, who managed city affairs.

00:09:44.519 --> 00:09:46.000
And the time of his death

00:09:46.159 --> 00:09:49.399
matched exactly with what was shown in the temple.

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:50.799
Ci'er.

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:53.720
Your name is also on that list.

00:09:54.960 --> 00:09:57.360
You must investigate this matter quickly.

00:09:58.399 --> 00:09:59.919
Otherwise, in a few days

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:01.279
I'm afraid

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:03.039
I'm afraid

00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:06.519
the Second Brother will also fall victim to the Ghost King.

00:10:06.519 --> 00:10:07.360
Second Brother.

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:09.519
I heard those who were killed

00:10:09.799 --> 00:10:12.360
had their bodies completely disfigured.

00:10:13.879 --> 00:10:15.639
The Ghost King is truly brutal.

00:10:16.600 --> 00:10:17.240
Second Brother,

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:20.120
you must be very careful, Second Brother.

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:20.879
Well...

00:10:21.559 --> 00:10:23.559
If I had Master Dongqing's skills,

00:10:24.080 --> 00:10:26.639
I would definitely defeat the Ghost King for you.

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:32.360
Dongqing.

00:10:33.279 --> 00:10:35.320
What do you think about this?

00:10:35.919 --> 00:10:36.639
Replying to Lord Father,

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.799
Ghosts and spirits may be frightening,

00:10:39.159 --> 00:10:40.720
but not as dangerous as the human heart.

00:10:41.639 --> 00:10:42.759
I believe behind all this

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:45.120
